from sysobjects
where id = object_id('busi_productpurchase')
and type = 'U')
drop table busi_productpurchase

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: busi_productpurchase */
/*==============================================================*/
create table busi_productpurchase (
ID int identity(1,1),
ProID int not null,
Link nvarchar(500) null,
IsDef bit null,
Price decimal(10,2) null,
SupplierID int null,
AppTime datetime not null default getdate(),
IsDel bit not null default 0,
constraint PK_BUSI_PRODUCTPURCHASE primary key (ID)
)
go
